      <title>[Letter] 1830 Jul. 18, Carthage, Tennessee [to] Joshua M. Coffee, Alexandria, Smith County, Tennessee / Adam Fergusson</title>
   </titleInfo>
   <abstract>This is a letter dated July 18, 1830 from Adam Fergusson in Carthage, Tennessee to Joshua M. Coffee in Alexandria, Tennessee. In the letter Fergusson informs Coffee of a rumor that the clerk of the County Court may resign his office, and that if this speculation is correct, he would like to be considered for the job.</abstract>
